{"tid":1700974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁樣我會番唔到工，唔好咁做。","createTime":"2019-11-08T18:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T16:28:55.000Z","uid":262116,"like":154,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"c485e02a31ff5ab9acee263efc884300e49ae215","tid":1700974,"uid":262116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:52:17.000Z","msg":"1.樓下巴士站出入口塞住我就出唔到去返工<br />\n<br />\n2.輕鐵路軌有嘢阻塞我都搭唔到輕鐵去返工<br />\n<br />\n3.西鐵地鐵雖然會開，但如果出口度有野塞有火燒緊，就算啲鐵開，我都搭唔到😭<br />\n<br />\n4.唔一定塞啲咩紅隧大欖個啲，如果啲停車場、屋村、私樓門口車道出口入比雜物阻塞，我又揸唔到車番工。<br />\n<br />\n5.唔好整啲假港鐵告示話暫停列車行使，我老母資訊唔流通會信晒架<br />\n<br />\n6.屋村實有啲位比人棄置傢俬，咪拎黎塞路呀<br />\n<br />\n到最後，唔番工啦唉，唔好咁做呀，我想番工。"},{"pid":"b642cc149dff7fc700616295b1337e6795c71776","tid":1700974,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:52:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入黎rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a3211860bc00ac246433c3258cad9de26e600c5a","tid":1700974,"uid":262116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T19:01:48.000Z","msg":"Ok?"},{"pid":"344d134a3b8981aaa6a6508dc3a5bf508a68b76c","tid":1700974,"uid":262116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3211860bc00ac246433c3258cad9de26e600c5a","tid":1700974,"uid":262116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T19:01:48.000Z","msg":"Ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T19:08:02.000Z","msg":"無人理😢"},{"pid":"62e1732c8b93ac0d3c2750864092624bf2a0e311","tid":1700974,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T19:30:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7407f3d28bb54a812def15d3119cdf33414a560a","tid":1700974,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:42:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2cb5229c18a8b744a78e98d715640d9161c4a3f","tid":1700974,"uid"