n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n巴士站或交通燈位都可<br />\n成本極低 安全性高 速度快過set rb<br />\n事後可清潔 就算要賠錢都大把人賠"},{"pid":"dd2f349937a264844cdb6bb87a783f5108743606","tid":1700974,"uid":189233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:59:46.000Z","msg":"岩啊"},{"pid":"313bedd6fb8420fa6f81bccaf8b40a43d916811b","tid":1700974,"uid":43033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c485e02a31ff5ab9acee263efc884300e49ae215","tid":1700974,"uid":262116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:52:17.000Z","msg":"1.樓下巴士站出入口塞住我就出唔到去返工<br />\n<br />\n2.輕鐵路軌有嘢阻塞我都搭唔到輕鐵去返工<br />\n<br />\n3.西鐵地鐵雖然會開，但如果出口度有野塞有火燒緊，就算啲鐵開，我都搭唔到😭<br />\n<br />\n4.唔一定塞啲咩紅隧大欖個啲，如果啲停車場、屋村、私樓門口車道出口入比雜物阻塞，我又揸唔到車番工。<br />\n<br />\n5.唔好整啲假港鐵告示話暫停列車行使，我老母資訊唔流通會信晒架<br />\n<br />\n6.屋村實有啲位比人棄置傢俬，咪拎黎塞路呀<br />\n<br />\n到最後，唔番工啦唉，唔好咁做呀，我想番工。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:42:25.000Z","msg":"上年 10號波第二日照返工呀  。<br />\n<br />\n港豬中意返工程度唔係咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n呢d碎料點會阻到港豬"},{"pid":"fe15ab4e575e61b61b658c7bc428744b348f2252","tid":1700974,"uid":43956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:55:11.000Z","msg":"屌 其實最簡單 係每部lift 上到最高 入去禁晒所有樓層 搞到佢層層停就掂啦 <br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好咁做 我想搭lift 落去翻工嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319775103b7686a3cdb1883fb24b6b8489ddbb43","tid":1700974,"uid":135845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T20:00:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3da40fa23b98c7428ef445f4f6c7ebd8ee9de45","tid":1700974,"uid":313764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T20:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cdzid4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cdzid4.png&h=568e94ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天氣一凍，好易有貓貓捐入車底取暖架!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702635\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702635</a>"},{"pid":"01b775f7f63de293a270f217faf4cfb36329fc08","tid":1700974,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c485e02a31ff5ab9acee263efc884300e49ae215","tid":1700974,"uid":262116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:52:17.000Z","msg":"1.樓下巴士站出入口塞住我就出唔到去返工<br />\n<br />\n2.輕鐵路軌有嘢阻塞我都搭唔到輕鐵去返工<br />\n<br />\n3.西鐵地鐵雖然會開，但如果出口度有野塞有火燒緊，就算啲鐵開，我都搭唔到😭<br />\n<br />\n4.唔一定塞啲咩紅隧大欖個啲，如果啲停車場、屋村、私樓門口車道出口入比雜物阻塞，我又揸唔到車番工。<br />\n<br />\n5.唔好整啲假港鐵告示話暫停列車行使，我老母資訊唔流通會信晒架<br />\n<br />\n6.屋村實有啲位比人棄置傢俬，咪拎黎塞路呀<br />\n<br />\n到最後，唔番工啦唉，唔好咁做呀，我想番工。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T20:39:13.000Z","msg":"但係馬路無巴士咪好暢通囉？<br />\n狗鐵就唔洗諗，一定自動收皮<br />\n隧道唔一定收費亭入口既，響出口受阻，都會好影響交通<br />\n<br />\n如果到時返唔到工，咪落樓下食個早餐返屋企瞓個靚覺，發個好夢囉"},{"pid":"c9b1f8227d80e4b9661431c18e3927917ca58d4d","tid":1700974,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T21:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUf59PR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUf59PR.jpg&h=6c38636e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b31ac7f12ed158c53f415f768519fe3f953e736b","tid":1700974,"uid":255686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T21:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9657dffcc5637a3abc0634dd2515713bf89142d3","tid":1700974,"uid":264215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T21:27:59.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好咁做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757f7a59cd696a91d1f08e99abb87d638c529e92","tid":1700974,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T21:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJnoWxS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u